Aim_crazyjump_v2

made by Axe to the D

Here it is... the new version of aim_crazyjump with several changes.

- new architecture
- new lightning
- texture fix
- and more...

The proportions of the crates are the same as in the old map. (Didnt copy anything)

To install put map into: C:\\Programm Files\\Steam\\steamapps\\*username*\\counter-strike source\\cstrike\\maps

Enjoy!
